{"tid":749214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果女朋友話驚被你飛左，所以自己走先，你有咩感想？","createTime":"2018-07-20T00:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:52:13.000Z","uid":77243,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7afeddee796829167f126875815912989c54d2c","tid":749214,"uid":77243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:40:16.000Z","msg":"話說同女朋友拍拖都半年，<br />\n自問自己唔係靚仔，<br />\n冇咩過人成就/能力，<br />\n亦唔係咩有錢富二代，<br />\n理應出面唔會有冇市場。<br />\n只知道自己係比較溫暖果D暖男type.<br />\n對女朋友特別好，非常照顧佢，<br />\n成日都會搵佢同佢報到，<br />\n佢唔夠安全感我就俾多D安存感佢。<br />\n但我女友就成日都好驚我會被人搶走，<br />\n又或者我會出軌，<br />\n所以一直都想同我講分手......<br />\n因為驚我會飛左佢。<br />\n咁佢連我呢D冇咩市場嘅男仔都可以冇信心，<br />\n佢係咪唔會拍到長拖...."},{"pid":"bd98ea695f1699f359c919dc5c0147a3f7b07196","tid":749214,"uid":121249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50839db0c2fb1df60973cce2adad2f059780a3c","tid":749214,"uid":85633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:42:13.000Z","msg":"咁分左未呢而家"},{"pid":"26af7e0ce2c08dbe8860166bc2606d2324e762df","tid":749214,"uid":78971,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:42:47.000Z","msg":"佢有一個更好嘅對象啫<br />\n唔洗深究太多"},{"pid":"928c49b2aac6026f87233b979b91dc64cec1d271","tid":749214,"uid":7240,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:43:01.000Z","msg":"我驚你俾綠帽我戴 所以我俾咗你戴先"},{"pid":"09df695dea8acaa7bce75355c85932bd81ee9698","tid":749214,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"你信咗呀，on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a7f088cc32fb230db653f70d38744fbc9847aa","tid":749214,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21db675b8805fb5d2322efa30bcf8b59dfe91605","tid":749214,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"咁既大話都信<br />\n一係你on9一係你on撚9"},{"pid":"2071b8d0a4b78a888bd2c45a0b53e1864cfd700a","tid":749214,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"人地有第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04bb7bf1b5cc60424761f975fcc4e8831af0cd1","tid":749214,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"對你冇安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9c02177a4e0b7d9a9adc369cef7d68c44a5f4","tid":749214,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:43:02.000Z","msg":"佢對第二個有feel"},{"pid":"26e2fa4e96c168986b7530fe1f836508e753a8a0","tid":749214,"uid":77243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"我信佢...但佢話佢唔識信我..所以覺得我會好辛苦....所以佢想走"},{"pid":"fceda3c4d1741dfe83d0fc579f78ad43e5cbb76b","tid":749214,"uid":77243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"佢自細長大嘅環境冇人關心照顧佢，<br />\n冇人教到佢點信人，<br />\n但佢信自己嘅時候往往都會受傷，<br />\n佢話因為我想佢信任我，<br />\n但佢唔識信我，<br />\n就驚我會飛左佢，<br />\n所以佢想飛左我先."},{"pid":"a8c5322ce1bf05552c96ac39326f7a3c0c46dc52","tid":749214,"uid":27729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">你咁好，係人都覺得配唔起你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"273d35924bfb0dedf45c996d1d4e029a7133241b","tid":749214,"uid":121395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:50:04.000Z","msg":"又真係好慘"},{"pid":"8310a10725c6851049071475e3f7a225944cf842","tid":749214,"uid":45037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8c5322ce1bf05552c96ac39326f7a3c0c46dc52","tid":749214,"uid":27729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">你咁好，係人都覺得配唔起你啦<im